olor'></span><a class='sd-link-color'></a></div></div>\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\t\n\t<div class=\"entry-links\">\n\t\t<p class=\"comment-number\"><a href=\"https://rottenindenmark.wordpress.com/2012/02/25/living-in-berlin-lesson-471/#respond\" title=\"Comment on Living in Berlin Lesson&nbsp;#471\">Leave a Comment</a></p>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"entry-categories tagged\">Filed under <a href=\"https://rottenindenmark.wordpress.com/category/germany/\" title=\"View all posts in Germany\" rel=\"category tag\">Germany</a>, <a href=\"https://rottenindenmark.wordpress.com/category/personal/\" title=\"View all posts in Personal\" rel=\"category tag\">Personal</a></p>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"entry-tags tagged\">Tagged as <a href=\"https://rottenindenmark.wordpress.com/tag/berlin/\" rel=\"tag\">berlin</a><br /></p>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .entry-links -->\n\n</div><!-- #post-## -->\n\n\n\n<div id=\"post-5189\" class=\"post-5189 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-america-2 category-journalism tag-watergate\">\n\t<div class=\"entry-meta\">\n\n\t\t &middot; 7:58 am\t</div><!-- .entry-meta -->\n\n\t<h2 class=\"entry-title\"><a href=\"https://rottenindenmark.wordpress.com/2012/02/25/why-did-deep-throat-leak-to-woodward/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Why Did Deep Throat Leak to&nbsp;Woodward?</a></h2>\t<div class=\"entry entry-content\">\n\t\t<p>I feel like the older I get, the more I realize that the answer to the question &#8216;Why did [historical figure] do [historic thing]?&#8217; always turns out to be &#8216;<a href=\"http://blogs.reuters.com/jackshafer/2012/02/21/what-made-deep-throat-leak/\">bald self-interest</a>&#8216;.</p>\n<div id=\"jp-post-flair\" class=\"sharedaddy sd-like-enabled sd-sharing-enabled\"><div class=\"sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled\"><div class=\"robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-icon-text sd-sharing\"><h3 class=\"sd-title\">Share this:</h3><div class=\"sd-content\"><ul><li class=\"share-facebook\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"sh