n>7 hours ago</span>\n    </p>\n\n    <div class=\"entry-body \">\n      \n\n\n\n        <p>I am evaluating possibilities for a potential project and one of those possibilities involve a mobile device with integrated NFC.</p>\r\n<p>It doesn't have to be a phone, but it has to be readily available in North America.</p>\r\n<p>The Nexus 7 comes to mind, but it's a bit on the expensive side for this project and something closer to iPod Touch size would be ideal. It should be decently fast, but performance isn't much of a concern.</p>\r\n<p>So basically there are three requirements: integrated NFC, 7 inch or smaller and around $150. Android isn't a strict requirement, but I'd rather stick to a widespread platform.</p>\r\n<p>Any ideas?</p>\n      <div class=\"article-meta clearfix\">\n  <ul class=\"simplelist sourcelist clearfix\">\n\n\n    \n\n  </ul>\n</div>\n\n\n    </div>\n\n\n\n    <div class=\"m-link-sets\">\n  <h2 class=\"verge-mobile-section\">More Stories</h2>\n  <ul>\n      <li><h3 class=\"stitle\"><a href=\"http://mobile.theverge.com/2014/2/5/5280920/tunnel-vision-bob-diamond-fights-for-the-atlantic-avenue-subway\">Tunnel vision: how an obsessed explorer found and lost the world's oldest&nbsp;subway</a></h3></li>\n      <li><h3 class=\"stitle\"><a href=\"http://mobile.theverge.com/2014/2/5/5361580/dayz-will-haunt-you\">Grim, broken, and grand: the mad world of&nbsp;'DayZ'</a></h3></li>\n      <li><h3 class=\"stitle\"><a href=\"http://mobile.theverge.com/2014/2/6/5385716/sony-vaio-iconic-pcs-photo-essay\">A look back at Sony's iconic VAIO&nbsp;computers</a></h3></li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n    <div id=\"comments\" class=\"comments_wrapper\"></div>\n\n<script type=\"script/template\" id=\"comment-account-actions-template\">\n    <div class=\"sign_up\">\n  <h2 class=\"vox-msg-join\">\n    Join the conversation!\n    <a href=\"#\" data-vox-auth=\"login\">Login</a> or <a href=\"#\" data-vox-auth=\"register\">sign up</a> to add your comment.\n  </h2>\n</div>\n\n</script>\